title: Fair Grounds Coffeehouse
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Fast food, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Previously all veg but no longer, as reported to happycow Oct 2012. Cozy coffee house and bakery with artwork displays. Extensive menu consists of breakfast foods, panini sandwiches, nachos, baked goods, tempeh, smoothies, and organic fair trade coffee. Vegan items are marked.
